WEBVTT

00:08:29.737 --> 00:08:31.140
(Laughter)

00:08:31.164 --> 00:08:34.618
And in an age where we have
too many choices,

00:08:35.075 --> 00:08:38.337
we have very little fear
of pregnancy and disease

00:08:38.361 --> 00:08:42.069
and we've got no feeling of shame
for sex before marriage,

00:08:42.093 --> 00:08:45.791
I think people are taking
their time to love.

00:08:46.408 --> 00:08:48.059
And actually, what's happening is,

00:08:48.083 --> 00:08:51.944
what we're seeing is a real expansion
of the precommitment stage

00:08:51.968 --> 00:08:53.704
before you tie the knot.

00:08:54.034 --> 00:08:56.760
Where marriage used to be
the beginning of a relationship,

00:08:56.784 --> 00:08:58.453
now it's the finale.

00:08:59.413 --> 00:09:01.153
But the human brain --